<HEADLINE> Russian Duma Confirms Putin as New Premier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, August 16 (Xinhua) -- The Russian State Duma on Monday
confirmed Vladimir Putin as the country's new prime minister, the
fifth in about 18 months.
</P>
