sovereignty and unification, and no form of separation will be
allowed, they said.
</P>
<P>
The Marine Corps is improving its landing skills on the South
China Sea during drills there, in spite of the mid-summer's
sweltering hot weather. They are demonstrating their determination
to defend the country's territorial integrity, as well as
displaying their military strength.
</P>
<P>
