S. troops stationed in South Korea. The flagship of the U.S. 7th
Fleet, the Blue Ridge, also participated in the maneuvers.
</P>
<P>
DPRK denounced the war game as "a war gamble targeting the
North" and urged the United States and South Korea to call off the
exercise. 
