<HEADLINE> Sautin Confident for Top Form at Sydney Olympics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, August 15 (Xinhua) -- Russian diving ace Dimitry Sautin
said here on Sunday he was confident for displaying his top form
at next year's Sydney Olympic Games.
</P>
<P>
"I will be in great shape, in very good form," Sautin told
Xinhua after winning the 10 meters platform at the Military World
Games here.
</P>
<P>
