second-placed Roman Volodkov of Ukraine at 631.68.
</P>
<P>
China's Liu Junhong was third at 613.62 while Peng Bo, who beat
Sautin to second in a springboard event, finished only fifth.
</P>
<P>
"I have a better form today," said Sautin, adding that his
secret for success was to practice.
</P>
<P>
"Only practice works," he said. 
